I assure you that I fully comprehend the gravity of this offense and the need to make amends. If given the opportunity, I am willing to undertake any necessary steps to improve myself and prevent any future transgressions. Whether it be attending a driving course or seeking additional education to address any underlying issues, I am dedicated to personal growth and ensuring that I never find myself in this position again.

